descriptionHTML:
Minimalist, black watch face inspired by TV series character Will Graham for Android Wear watches.

Details of design:

→ White background
→ Black wireframe clock face

→ Support for Android Wear devices ONLY (i.e. NOT Samsung Gear 2, S, Fit etc.)
